<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Colorado Springs Sim Racing</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@500;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
body{
    margin:0;
    background:#0a0a0a;
    color:white;
    font-family:Inter,sans-serif;
}

.hero{
    height:100vh;
    position:relative;
    overflow:hidden;
}

.hero video{
    position:absolute;
    width:100%;
    height:100%;
    object-fit:cover;
    opacity:.35;
}

.overlay{
    position:relative;
    z-index:2;
    height:100%;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px;
}

h1{
    font-family:Orbitron,sans-serif;
    font-size:4rem;
    max-width:900px;
}

.btn{
    margin-top:20px;
    background:#e10600;
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    padding:15px 35px;
    border-radius:8px;
}

.section{
    max-width:1100px;
    margin:auto;
    padding:80px 20px;
}

.cards{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
    gap:20px;
}

.card{
    background:#151515;
    padding:30px;
    border-radius:12px;
}

form{
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    gap:15px;
}

input, textarea{
    background:#1c1c1c;
    border:none;
    color:white;
    padding:15px;
    border-radius:8px;
}

button{
    background:#e10600;
    color:white;
    border:none;
    padding:15px;
    border-radius:8px;
    cursor:pointer;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<section class="hero">
    <video autoplay muted loop playsinline>
        <source src="hero-video.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    </video>

    <div class="overlay">
        <h1>Colorado Springs' Home for Competitive Sim Racing</h1>

        <p>
            Professional simulators. Endurance racing.
            Family-friendly competition.
        </p>

        <a href="#signup" class="btn">Join the Launch List</a>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <div class="cards">

        <div class="card">
            <h2>Professional Simulators</h2>
            <p>
                Premium direct-drive racing systems designed
                for realistic endurance racing experiences.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>Competitive Events</h2>
            <p>
                Weekly leagues, championships, endurance races,
                and special tournaments.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h2>Family Friendly</h2>
            <p>
                No experience required. We’ll teach you everything you need to get on track — from your first lap to your first win.
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <h2>Our Vision</h2>

    <p>
        We're building a community-focused sim racing center in
        Colorado Springs centered around Le Mans Ultimate,
        endurance racing, and organized competition.
    </p>
</section>

<section id="signup" class="section">
    <h2>Be First on the Grid</h2>

    <form action="YOUR_FORMSPREE_URL" method="POST">

        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Name">

        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email">

        <textarea
            name="comments"
            placeholder="What events would you like to see?">
        </textarea>

        <button type="submit">
            Notify Me When You Open
        </button>

    </form>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <h2>Founding Members</h2>

    <p>
        Join the launch list for updates, early access opportunities,
        and future league announcements.
    </p>
</section>

</body>
</html>
